description:
This is a 17 minute workout called 'My BEST Pilates Lower Body Exercises | 15 min At Home Pilates Workout' from the channel Lilly Sabri.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Light.

It's an intense 15 minute at home pilates butt and leg workout that includes all my favourite and most effective lower body movements that I have learnt over the years. I challenge you to do this for 14 days and let me know how you do in the comments down below!
